<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.8">
<l>patta rāviyaip pāṉmati yaiyaṇit</l>
<l>tottai māliruñ cōlaito ḻutupōy</l>
<l>mutti ṉaimaṇi yaimaṇi māṇikka</l>
<l>vitti ṉaiceṉṟu viṇṇakar kāṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone, worshipping [the one who is] the soul of the bhaktas,</l>
<l>The milky moon, a cluster of gems in Māliruñcōlai,</l>
<l>We will go and see the pearl, the jewel,</l>
<l>The jeweled ruby, the sage in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
